content:
Tech stocks surged while Russia-Ukraine fears pressured the broader mkt.

Nasdaq +1.9% after Elon Musk took a 9.2% stake in $TWTR, which soared 27% to $49.93.

But Dow ends up just 103, +0.3% to 34,921. S&P +0.8% while 7 of 11 S&P stock sectors fell.

U.S. oil +3.9% to $103.11
renderedContent:
Tech stocks surged while Russia-Ukraine fears pressured the broader mkt.

Nasdaq +1.9% after Elon Musk took a 9.2% stake in $TWTR, which soared 27% to $49.93.

But Dow ends up just 103, +0.3% to 34,921. S&P +0.8% while 7 of 11 S&P stock sectors fell.

U.S. oil +3.9% to $103.11
